---
title: Tex-Mex Spiced Pork & Leafy Rice with Cucumber Salsa & Mayo
description: This colourful Tex-Mex dish ticks every box. With a warming spice blend, plus creamy mayo and speedy rice with baby leaves stirred through, your tastebuds are fully catered for, as they should be!

